---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Discord"
description: "Rejoins la communauté LIBRAW sur Discord — aide, partage de ressources, discussions tech."
permalink: /discord/
---

<div class="page-wrapper discord-page">

  {# ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="discord-hero">
    <div class="discord-hero-icon">
      <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="discord-hero-text">
      <span class="page-eyebrow">// communauté</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Rejoins le Discord</h1>
      <p class="page-description">Pose tes questions, partage des ressources, suis les mises à jour du site. La communauté FR autour de LIBRAW.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/wSgQhhRjBy" class="discord-join-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Rejoindre le serveur
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="discord-divider"></div>

  {# ─── Ce qu'on trouve sur le serveur ──────────────────────── #}
  <div class="discord-section">
    <span class="section-label">// salons</span>
    <h2 class="discord-section-title">Ce qu'il y a sur le serveur</h2>

    <div class="discord-channels">

      <div class="discord-channel-group">
        <span class="channel-group-label">📋 Accueil</span>
        <div class="channel-list">
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">règles</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Les règles du serveur — à lire avant de participer</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">annonces</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Nouvelles ressources, guides, mises à jour du site</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">rôles</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Choisis tes catégories pour les notifs</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="discord-channel-group">
        <span class="channel-group-label">💬 Général</span>
        <div class="channel-list">
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">général</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Discussion tech, piratage, outils</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">aide-générale</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Questions sur les ressources et guides du site</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">partage</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Ressources et liens à partager avec la communauté</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="discord-channel-group">
        <span class="channel-group-label">🗂️ Catégories</span>
        <div class="channel-list">
          {% for cat in site.categories %}
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-emoji">{{ cat.emoji }}</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">{{ cat.slug }}</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">{{ cat.description }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="discord-channel-group">
        <span class="channel-group-label">📖 Guides</span>
        <div class="channel-list">
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">discussion-guides</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Retours, erreurs, suggestions sur les guides publiés</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-hash">#</span>
            <div class="channel-body">
              <span class="channel-name">propositions</span>
              <span class="channel-desc">Propose une ressource ou un guide à ajouter au site</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="discord-divider"></div>

  {# ─── Rôles ────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="discord-section">
    <span class="section-label">// rôles</span>
    <h2 class="discord-section-title">Les rôles disponibles</h2>

    <div class="discord-roles">
      <div class="discord-role">
        <span class="role-badge" style="color:#f87171;border-color:rgba(248,113,113,.3)">⚡ Admin</span>
        <span class="role-desc">Gestion du serveur et du site</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discord-role">
        <span class="role-badge" style="color:#fb923c;border-color:rgba(251,146,60,.3)">🔧 Modérateur</span>
        <span class="role-desc">Modération quotidienne</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discord-role">
        <span class="role-badge" style="color:#6c8eff;border-color:rgba(108,142,255,.3)">📖 Contributeur</span>
        <span class="role-desc">A proposé une ressource ou un guide accepté sur le site</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discord-role">
        <span class="role-badge" style="color:#a78bfa;border-color:rgba(167,139,250,.3)">⭐ Habitué</span>
        <span class="role-desc">Membre actif du serveur</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discord-role">
        <span class="role-badge" style="color:#8b93a8;border-color:rgba(139,147,168,.3)">👶 Nouveau</span>
        <span class="role-desc">Attribué automatiquement à l'arrivée</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="discord-roles-note">
      Des rôles opt-in par catégorie sont disponibles dans <span class="accent">#rôles</span> pour recevoir uniquement les notifs qui t'intéressent.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="discord-divider"></div>

  {# ─── CTA final ────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="discord-cta">
    <p class="discord-cta-text">// discord.gg/wSgQhhRjBy</p>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/wSgQhhRjBy" class="discord-join-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Rejoindre le serveur
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>

</div>
